This is implementation of firewall in p4lang.
In this experiment I am using p4 lang's bloom filter construct.
Bloom filter is used as a hash.If bloom filter has seen certain hash <srcIP,dstIP,srcPort,dstPort> before then it lets pass through packet.
Otherwise it drops it. while packet going from inside to outside the bloom filter is populated.
While packet coming from outside to inside bloom filter is checked.
